snippet.title: Amber Heard - Artwork for Sale
snippet.description:
Amber Heard artwork for sale - "worded ink drawing" made out of words to create the lines and shading.

Full details: http://www.zerogravityartwork.com/art-for-sale/amber-heard-worded-ink-drawing/edmonton-AB/21

Museum quality canvas prints are available, as well as posters. Drawn by artist Francine Mercier from Zero Gravity Artwork, based in Edmonton, Alberta, Canada.

Shop online at www.ZeroGravityArtwork.com to order your print today. Worldwide shipping is available.
